## Analysis

Here's a plot...

```{r preview = TRUE}
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Width, y = Petal.Length)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = Species))
```


Here's a table...

```{r}
iris %>%
  group_by(Species) %>% 
  summarize(mean_Petal_Length = mean(Petal.Length)) %>% 
  rmarkdown::paged_table()
```
